SELECT
    TrackId,
    Genre.Name AS Genre,
    Artist.Name AS Artist,
    Album.Title AS Album,
    Track.Name AS Track
FROM
    Track
INNER JOIN
    Artist ON Artist.ArtistId = Album.ArtistId,
    Album ON Album.AlbumId = Track.AlbumId,
    Genre ON Genre.GenreId = Track.GenreId
;
